high_descs: Turn left and head to the left side of the dining table.
Pick up the head of lettuce on the left.
Turn right and walk forward to the sink.
Put the lettuce in the sink, rinse it off, and take it back out.
Turn around and walk to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, place the lettuce to the right of the bowl, and close the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned head of lettuce in a refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn around, walk to door, turn right, walk to table.
Pick up the lettuce to the left, sitting on the spoon.
Turn right, walk to sink, turn left, take 1 step, turn right to face between the sink and counter.
Place lettuce in sink, turn water on to rinse lettuce, turn water back off, pick up the lettuce.
Turn around and walk to the wall.  Turn left and walk to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator doors, place lettuce on the top right shelf, to the right of the bowl, shut the refrigerator doors.
anns.task_desc: Wash the lettuce and put it in the refrigerator.

high_descs: pick up a lettuce head from the table
turn right and head towards the sink
wash the lettuce head in the sink
turn around and locate the fridge
place the lettuce head in the fridge
anns.task_desc: drop a clean lettuce head in the fridge
